Well, here we are in a kitchen. You can barely contain your excitement.

You can see an open fridge here. The fridge contains a cilantro, a yellow bell pepper, a block of cheese, a parsley and some water. You scan the room for an oven, and you find an oven. Look over there! a table. You see a knife on the table. What's that over there? It looks like it's a counter. The counter is vast. On the counter you make out a red apple, a raw purple potato, a red onion and a cookbook. You can make out a stove. The stove is conventional. But the thing is empty. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the stove.

There is an open plain door leading north. You don't like doors? Why not try going east, that entranceway is not blocked by one.

On the counter you make out a red apple, a raw purple potato, a red onion and a cookbook. You can make out a stove. The stove is conventional. But the thing is empty. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the stove.

There is an open plain door leading north. You don't like doors? Why not try going east, that entranceway is not blocked by one.
